{
  "stem": "1160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was always so good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We always relied on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My grandparents, my mother's parents, adored him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Her sisters, her brothers adored him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a very good person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was healthy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nothing wrong with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His problem was that he was born Jewish, [SOBBING] so he was killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One man came back-- this was the only one who came back to Hajdunanas who was with my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this man-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was-- he was a ter-- he was almost a nervous wreck already.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a very nice man, but you could tell that he went through a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once he told us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that they were marching in the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was in the Ukraine, I guess, in the [INAUDIBLE], the [INAUDIBLE] river.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were walking and walking, and suddenly the bombs was falling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when he got up from the floor-- from the dirt, he says nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The earth swallowed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's-- that's what we know about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was my uncle, my mother's brother was there also with my father, Moishe Safar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were the same age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the earth swallowed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] It is a labor battalion, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in '42, that's where they took them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's where they-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so they had been sent to the front and-- where the bombs had--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know the details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is how much I know, and that he didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- and this man said that they suffered a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
